 50s 
 50s        -q, --quiet
 50s               Quiet operation  (default=off)
 50s 
 50s        -v, --verbose
 50s               Produce more output  (default=off)
 50s 
 50s        Selecting one of the following modes is required:
 50s 
 50s               Mode: info
 50s 
 50s        -i, --info
 50s               Parse and print human readable summary of PSKC input (default=off)
 50s 
 50s               Mode: validate
 50s 
 50s        -e, --validate
 50s               Validate PSKC input against XML Schema  (default=off)
 50s 
 50s               Mode: sign
 50s 
