 50s 
 50s        --sign-key=FILE
 50s               Private key to sign with
 50s 
 50s        --sign-crt=FILE
 50s               X.509 certificate to sign with
 50s 
 50s               Mode: verify
 50s 
 50s               Verify digitally signed PSKC data
 50s 
 50s        --verify
 50s               Verify signed PSKC input  (default=off)
 50s 
 50s        --verify-crt=FILE
